{"tid":1288158,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警方」拘捕涉嫌公開警員私隱者 遭起底警員資料源自親中名校","createTime":"2019-07-05T13:32:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T20:44:41.000Z","uid":199376,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a1fea63c40d018597ae46dd683826126cc6a5f02","tid":1288158,"uid":199376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T13:32:09.000Z","msg":"反送中示威引發連串衝突及警員遭起底的爭議，警方網絡安全及科技罪案調查科接手調查後近日拘捕至少9人，其中一名被捕人，就是早前涉嫌在網上公開628名警員的私隱包括全名、手機號碼及住址，並自稱屬於國際黑客組織「匿名者（Anonymous）」的男子，他目前已獲准保釋候查，須於8月上旬向警方報到。消息稱，被捕男子是一間親中直資名校的電腦技術員，他涉嫌在學校資料庫搜尋出逾628名曾為子女報讀該校的警察父母的資料，再於網上公開，結果他被警方查出身份。據悉警方是以他涉嫌違反《個人資料（私隱）條例》第64條拘捕他，該罪行刑罰甚重，若罪成最高可判監5年及罰款100萬。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"200663b26e1542c775e929bbcaa7e38ed1bc2590","tid":1288158,"uid":199376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T13:32:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://ahknews.com/r/e2JD3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fahknews.com%2Fr%2Fe2JD3&d=TgwWsw16K2C65RuBgL3vHU4axDeVXns42j9POfnWuxs%3D&h=a7727e13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://ahknews.com/r/e2JD3</a>"},{"pid":"1fbe2bd77e2d24e493dc295336de7a2a5963de6d","tid":1288158,"uid":199376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T13:35:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"68ecd3bf4fb0ec0ea3002cf710ecd5c8a42c00b6","tid":1288158,"uid":199376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T13:35:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c0d781d92239ad305d198977252bb208da8d1242","tid":1288158,"uid":199376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T13:36:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f19ec498efaf34438ec8044fa6ff211e0c46c093","tid":1288158,"uid":199376,"like":0,"d